---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Lesotho — The Kingdom in the Sky | MPLS LLC" description="A tribute to the Kingdom of Lesotho, the nation behind the .ls domain. MPLS LLC honors the Basotho people, their heritage, and their beautiful mountain kingdom.">

	<!-- Hero -->
	<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute inset-0">
			<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Early_Morning_view_from_Sehlabathebe_House_-_panoramio.jpg/1280px-Early_Morning_view_from_Sehlabathebe_House_-_panoramio.jpg" alt="Lesotho highlands landscape" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-950/90 via-emerald-900/80 to-emerald-950/60"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-12 pb-16 md:pb-20 lg:pb-24 w-full">
			<div class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-12">
				<!-- Left: Intro text -->
				<div class="lg:flex-1 text-center lg:text-left mb-12 lg:mb-0">
					<p class="reveal text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 mb-4">Why .ls?</p>
					<h1 class="reveal delay-1 font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-[1.1]">
						The Kingdom<br/>in the Sky
					</h1>
					<p class="reveal delay-2 mt-6 text-lg text-emerald-100/90 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
						Our domain <strong class="text-white">mp.ls</strong> uses the <strong class="text-white">.ls</strong> country code top-level domain, which belongs to the <strong class="text-white">Kingdom of Lesotho</strong>, a landlocked nation of breathtaking mountains, resilient people, and a rich cultural heritage.
					</p>
					<div class="reveal delay-3 mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
						<a href="#about" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">
							Explore the Kingdom
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5 12 21m0 0-7.5-7.5M12 21V3" /></svg>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- Right: Donate widget -->
				<div class="reveal from-right delay-2 lg:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0">
					<div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/20 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
						<div class="bg-white/10 px-6 py-5 text-center border-b border-white/10">
							<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 mb-1">Give Back</p>
							<h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white sm:text-2xl">Support Lesotho</h2>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6">
							<p class="text-emerald-100/80 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-4">
								Words of appreciation are a start, but action speaks louder. Support education, healthcare, and community development in Lesotho.
							</p>
							<a href="https://www.every.org/help-lesotho/f/help-lesotho" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full rounded-xl bg-white px-6 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-emerald-800 hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z" /></svg>
								Donate Now
								<svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" /></svg>
							</a>
							<p class="text-xs text-emerald-300/50 text-center mt-4">
								Powered by <a href="https://www.every.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">Every.org</a>. 501(c)(3) nonprofit. Tax-deductible in the US.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Flag & Quick Facts -->
	<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="lg:flex lg:items-start lg:gap-16">
				<!-- Flag + landscape image -->
				<div class="reveal from-left lg:flex-1 mb-12 lg:mb-0 space-y-6">
					<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-zinc-200">
						<div class="aspect-[3/2] relative flex flex-col">
							<div class="flex-1 bg-[#00209F]"></div>
							<div class="flex-1 bg-white flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 200 120" class="h-20 w-auto" fill="none">
									<path d="M100 10 L30 100 L170 100 Z" fill="black" stroke="black" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
									<line x1="20" y1="100" x2="180" y2="100" stroke="black" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div class="flex-1 bg-[#009543]"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 italic">Flag of the Kingdom of Lesotho, featuring the mokorotlo, the traditional Basotho straw hat</p>
					<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
						<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ce/Roman_Catholic_Archdiocese_of_Maseru.jpg/960px-Roman_Catholic_Archdiocese_of_Maseru.jpg" alt="Maseru, capital city of Lesotho" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-3">
							<p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 italic">Maseru, capital of the Kingdom of Lesotho</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Quick facts -->
				<div class="reveal from-right delay-2 lg:flex-1">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-600 mb-3">At a Glance</p>
					<h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 sm:text-4xl mb-8">Lesotho</h2>
					<div class="space-y-5">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 0 0 8.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 0 1-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 0 1 7.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 0 0-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0 1 12 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0 1 21 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0 1 12 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Official Name</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Kingdom of Lesotho (Muso oa Lesotho)</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Capital</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Maseru</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Population</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">~2.3 million people</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 21l5.25-11.25L21 21m-9-3h7.5M3 5.621a48.474 48.474 0 016-.371m0 0c1.12 0 2.233.038 3.334.114M9 5.25V3m3.334 2.364V3" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Languages</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Sesotho &amp; English (official)</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Currency</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Lesotho loti (plural: maloti)</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Founded</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">1822 by King Moshoeshoe I. Independent since 1966</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15M5.25 3v18m13.5-18v18M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21" /></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Government</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Parliamentary constitutional monarchy under King Letsie III</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Parallax Image Band -->
	<section class="relative h-72 md:h-96 overflow-hidden">
		<div class="parallax-bg absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Snow_Capped_Maloti_Mountains_-_panoramio.jpg/1280px-Snow_Capped_Maloti_Mountains_-_panoramio.jpg');">
		</div>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-transparent to-zinc-50"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6 md:p-10">
			<p class="reveal text-white text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase drop-shadow-lg">Maloti Mountains, Lesotho</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The Land -->
	<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-zinc-50">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="reveal max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-600 mb-3">Geography</p>
				<h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 sm:text-4xl">A Country Above the Clouds</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
					Lesotho is the only independent state in the world that lies <strong>entirely above 1,000 metres</strong> in elevation. Its lowest point (1,400 metres) is the highest lowest point of any country on Earth.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="reveal delay-1 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
					<div class="h-44 overflow-hidden">
						<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Landscape_in_the_Mountain_Kingdom.jpg/1280px-Landscape_in_the_Mountain_Kingdom.jpg" alt="Thabana Ntlenyana peak" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" loading="lazy" />
					</div>
					<div class="p-8 text-center">
						<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-2">3,482m</p>
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Thabana Ntlenyana</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Highest peak in Southern Africa, located in Lesotho's Maloti Mountains</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="reveal delay-2 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
					<div class="h-44 overflow-hidden">
						<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/Katse_Dam-001.jpg/1280px-Katse_Dam-001.jpg" alt="Satellite view of Lesotho" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" loading="lazy" />
					</div>
					<div class="p-8 text-center">
						<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">30,355 km&sup2;</p>
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Entirely Landlocked</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Completely surrounded by South Africa, the largest such sovereign enclave in the world</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="reveal delay-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
					<div class="h-44 overflow-hidden">
						<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/66/Unnamed_Road%2C_Lesotho_-_panoramio_%2816%29.jpg/1280px-Unnamed_Road%2C_Lesotho_-_panoramio_%2816%29.jpg" alt="Snow in the Lesotho highlands" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" loading="lazy" />
					</div>
					<div class="p-8 text-center">
						<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-violet-800 mb-2">80%+</p>
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Above 1,800m</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Over 80% of the country lies above 1,800 metres, with snowfall common in the highlands</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- People Image Band -->
	<section class="relative h-64 md:h-80 overflow-hidden">
		<div class="parallax-bg absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/King_Moshoeshoe_of_the_Basotho_with_his_ministers.jpg/1280px-King_Moshoeshoe_of_the_Basotho_with_his_ministers.jpg');">
		</div>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-50 via-transparent to-white"></div>
	</section>

	<!-- The People -->
	<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="lg:flex lg:items-start lg:gap-16">
				<div class="reveal from-left lg:flex-1 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-600 mb-3">The Basotho</p>
					<h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 sm:text-4xl">A People of Resilience &amp; Unity</h2>
					<p class="mt-6 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
						The Basotho people (singular: Mosotho) make up 99.7% of Lesotho's population, making it one of the most ethnically unified nations in Africa. In a continent where colonial borders often split ethnic groups across multiple countries, Lesotho stands as a rare nation-state where the boundaries reflect a single people's identity.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
						The nation was forged in the early 1800s by <strong>King Moshoeshoe I</strong>, a visionary leader who united rival clans and former adversaries into a single polity at Butha-Buthe Mountain. His diplomatic skill in seeking British protection against Boer encroachment in 1868 preserved the sovereignty that would eventually become independence in 1966.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
						Lesotho holds one of the <strong>highest literacy rates in Africa</strong>, with women's literacy (85%) notably exceeding men's (68%). The country invests over 12% of its GDP in education, a reflection of values that run deep in Basotho culture.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
						<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/67/685_Thaba_Bosiu.jpg/960px-685_Thaba_Bosiu.jpg" alt="Thaba Bosiu, mountain fortress of King Moshoeshoe I" class="w-full h-56 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-3">
							<p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 italic">Thaba Bosiu, mountain fortress of King Moshoeshoe I, birthplace of the Basotho nation</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="reveal from-right delay-2 lg:flex-1">
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 p-6">
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
								<span class="text-2xl">🎵</span> National Anthem
							</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed italic">"Lesotho fatše la bo-ntat'a rona"</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1 mb-3">"Lesotho, Land of Our Fathers"</p>
							<audio controls preload="none" class="w-full h-10 rounded-lg">
								<source src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/aa/National_anthem_of_Lesotho%2C_performed_by_the_U.S._Navy_Band.wav" type="audio/wav" />
							</audio>
							<p class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mt-2">Performed by the U.S. Navy Band</p>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden">
							<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e1/Maluti_snow.jpg" alt="Snow-capped Maloti Mountains, Lesotho" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
							<div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6">
								<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
									<span class="text-2xl">🏔️</span> The Maloti Mountains
								</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">The dramatic highland range that defines Lesotho's landscape. Home to alpine grasslands, the endemic spiral aloe (<em>Aloe polyphylla</em>), and the Afriski resort, one of only two ski resorts in all of sub-Saharan Africa.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden">
							<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/62/Let%C5%A1eng_Diamond_Mine.jpg" alt="Letšeng Diamond Mine, Lesotho" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
							<div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6">
								<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
									<span class="text-2xl">💎</span> Diamonds &amp; Water
								</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">Lesotho's natural treasures include some of the world's most valuable diamonds. The Letšeng mine produces gems with an average value of over $2,000 per carat. The Lesotho Highlands Water Project supplies water to millions in South Africa.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden">
							<div class="bg-zinc-100 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
								<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/41/Wakanda_Flag.svg" alt="Flag of Wakanda" class="h-28 w-auto" loading="lazy" />
							</div>
							<div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6">
								<h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
									<span class="text-2xl">🎬</span> Wakanda Connection
								</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">Director Ryan Coogler stated that his depiction of Wakanda in <em>Black Panther</em> (2018) was inspired by Lesotho. The iconic Basotho blankets featured in the film became more widely known as a result.</p>
