				</div>
				<div class="p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">The Mokorotlo</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-emerald-200 leading-relaxed">The traditional conical straw hat, called the mokorotlo, is so central to Basotho identity that it appears on the national flag. Its distinctive shape is said to represent the mountain of Qiloane near the old capital of Thaba Bosiu.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="culture-card rounded-2xl border border-emerald-800 bg-emerald-900/60 overflow-hidden">
				<div class="h-48 overflow-hidden bg-emerald-800/40">
